    "In federated environments, feature engineering must address the challenge of extracting meaningful insights from data, while ensuring alignment with the privacy-preserving and decentralized nature of federated learning.",
    "Neural network architectures, particularly deep learning models, significantly enhance the detection of malicious clients by learning complex patterns and relationships in the data.",
    "When combined with advanced feature engineering techniques, their effectiveness is further amplified.",
    "Research on feature engineering-based IDS has explored diverse approaches to applying feature engineering.",
    "This diversity is evident from the use of multiple methods for engineering features."
